name: Nalan Cheel
Lore: 'Male Bith musician. Though he enjoys playing his Bandfill in Figrin D''an''s band, he misses the bubblink pink swamps of his homeworld, Clak''dor VII.',
Text: 'After using Bith Shuffle, peek at top X cards of pile or deck just shuffled, where X = number of other musicians at same site. May reshuffle without peeking.',
